@page "/"
@layout MainLayout

<h1>Hello, Cosmo!</h1>

<p>Welcome to the comprehensive <strong>CosmoKitchenSink</strong> sample application. This project demonstrates all the Blazor-like features currently supported by CosmoApiServer.</p>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <Card Title="Core Components" Link="/counter" Header="Framework Base" Width="100%">
            <p>Leverage the custom <code>ComponentBase</code> for lifecycle methods and state management.</p>
            <ul>
                <li><code>OnInitializedAsync</code></li>
                <li><code>OnParametersSetAsync</code></li>
                <li><code>BuildRenderTreeAsync</code></li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/counter" class="btn btn-outline-primary mt-2">Try Counter Demo</a>
        </Card>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <Card Title="Form System" Link="/forms" Header="Validation & Inputs" Width="100%">
            <p>Full support for <code>EditForm</code> and standard input components with DataAnnotations validation.</p>
            <a href="/forms" class="btn btn-primary mt-2">Try Forms & Validation</a>
        </Card>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row mt-4">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <Card Title="Cascading Values" Link="/cascading" Width="100%">
            <p>Pass data down the component tree without explicit parameters.</p>
            <a href="/cascading" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn More</a>
        </Card>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <Card Title="Route Parameters" Link="/user/1" Width="100%">
            <p>Dynamic routing with typed parameters from the URL.</p>
            <a href="/user/1" class="btn btn-secondary">View Profile</a>
        </Card>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <Card Title="Async Loading" Link="/fetchdata" Width="100%">
            <p>Seamlessly inject and use services to load data asynchronously.</p>
            <a href="/fetchdata" class="btn btn-secondary">Fetch Data</a>
        </Card>
    </div>
</div>
